<div class="content" name="USER_SESSION_KEY" uuid="9c07428c-a907-4590-a2c1-bb95a009e527"><p>The <b>USER_SESSION_KEY</b> structure defines an encrypted
user <span><a href="b5e7d25a-40b2-41c8-9611-98f53358af66#gt_4f67a585-fb00-4166-93e8-cf4abca8226d" data-linktype="relative-path">session
key</a></span>.</p><dl>
<dd>
<div><pre> typedef struct _USER_SESSION_KEY {
   CYPHER_BLOCK data[2];
 } USER_SESSION_KEY,
  *PUSER_SESSION_KEY;
</pre></div>
</dd></dl><p><b>data:</b> A two-element <b>CYPHER_BLOCK</b>
structure, as specified in section <span><a href="56a8d298-dbeb-4eb5-ad98-76536ec352f8" data-linktype="relative-path">2.2.1.1.1</a></span>, that
contains the 16-byte encrypted user session key.</p></div>